snippet.textDisplay: I think xulfi should introduce classical instrumental musical experiences to this season. You know coke studios legacy is all about classic. Bollywood and South have plenty of these melodies. though it is my very personal opinion. But would say these songs in this season are fresh but  I would dare to say I wouldn't come back to hear these songs years after year like I do come for jugni, allahu, chap tilak , saien zahoor, muzammel haque, Abu Muhammad, Javed bashir , RFAK, rizawan &muazzam. Believe we don't come here for melody here we come for house of music. Present those jewels dear xulfi. otherwise it would go like many million other melodias song platform who come and go. Though I would admit that this season songs so far very new and extraordinary one after another.
